## 5. Feature Requirements

### 5.1 Authentication & User Management
**Priority: P0 (Must Have)**

- User registration with name, email, phone, password, and role (Farmer / Buyer)
- JWT-based login with 7-day token expiry
- Role-based access control (farmers list crops; buyers bid/buy)
- Profile management (update name, contact, location, profile photo)
- Password reset via email

### 5.2 AI Crop Disease Detection
**Priority: P0 (Must Have)**

- Upload leaf photo via camera or gallery
- MobileNetV2 CNN model classifies disease from 38 classes across 14 crops
- Returns: disease name, confidence score, treatment recommendation
- Detection history stored per user
- Voice-based image upload trigger (P1)
- Demo mode fallback when model unavailable

### 5.3 Digital Marketplace
**Priority: P0 (Must Have)**

- Farmers create crop listings with: name, quantity, price/unit, location, harvest date, photos
- Buyers browse listings with search and category filters
- Real-time bidding via Socket.IO
- Listing expiry management
- Farmer dashboard to track listings and bids received

### 5.4 Order Management
**Priority: P0 (Must Have)**

- Buyer places order for a listing
- Order lifecycle: Placed → Confirmed → Shipped → Delivered / Cancelled
- Payment integration via Razorpay (test & live modes)
- Order history for both farmers and buyers
- Email/in-app notifications on status changes

### 5.5 Agri Store
**Priority: P1 (Should Have)**

- Product catalog: seeds, fertilizers, pesticides, tools
- Category-based browsing
- Cart and checkout with Razorpay payment
- Inventory management by admin
- Product detail pages with usage instructions

### 5.6 Crop Insurance
**Priority: P1 (Should Have)**

- Browse government and private insurance schemes
- Filter by crop type, region, premium amount
- View scheme details (coverage, eligibility, documents required)
- Apply/express interest (redirect to official scheme portal or in-app form)

### 5.7 AI Chat Support
**Priority: P1 (Should Have)**

- 24/7 AI farming assistant (Claude/GPT integration)
- Context-aware responses for farming queries
- Multilingual support (English, Hindi, Marathi)
- Chat history stored per session

### 5.8 Krishi Samachar (News & Prices)
**Priority: P1 (Should Have)**

- Live agricultural news feed from external APIs
- Daily mandi (market) price updates by crop and region
- Weather widget for user's location

### 5.9 Multilingual Support
**Priority: P0 (Must Have)**

- English, Hindi, Marathi via i18next
- Language preference stored in user profile
- All UI labels, error messages, and notifications translated

### 5.10 Voice Commands
**Priority: P2 (Nice to Have)**

- Voice-triggered crop listing upload
- Voice navigation for key app flows
- Web Speech API integration

