## 6. Non-Functional Requirements

| Category | Requirement |
|---|---|
| Performance | Page load < 3s on 4G; AI detection < 10s |
| Availability | 99.5% uptime target |
| Scalability | Support 10,000 concurrent users |
| Security | JWT auth, HTTPS, input sanitization, rate limiting |
| Accessibility | WCAG 2.1 AA compliance, keyboard navigation |
| Localization | RTL layout consideration for future languages |
| Mobile | Responsive design, PWA-ready |

---

## 7. Constraints & Assumptions

- Target devices: mid-range Android smartphones (primary), desktop (secondary)
- Internet connectivity: 4G/LTE assumed; offline PWA for future phase
- Razorpay available only for Indian payment methods
- AI model accuracy depends on PlantVillage dataset (14 crop types)
- Demo mode ensures AI service remains usable without a trained model

---

## 8. Out of Scope (v1)

- iOS/Android native apps
- Offline-first mode
- Logistics/delivery tracking integration
- Farmer credit/loan features
- Automated government scheme integration via APIs

